# JIRA BUG AGENT RULE

## Rule JIRA.0: Scope and Prohibition

**Allowed:** Create or rewrite Jira bugs on the **Experiments** board only, using the standard template (Summary, Description, Steps to reproduce, Expected result, Actual result, Environment, Technical details, Example).

**PROHIBITED:** Creating or writing Jira bugs in **Phoenix delivery**. Any such request MUST be blocked. Hooks enforce this.
